    "Introduced in Nature Journal on October 19, 2017, AlphaGo Zero is a nextlevel version of the Go software created without using data from human games, stronger than any previous version (Silver et al., 2017).",
    "By playing games against itself, AlphaGo Zero exceeded all the old versions of AlphaGo in 40 days (AlphaGo, 2023b).",
